Package grisu.jcommons.constants

Provides a location to set constants that may or not be used across several grid clients.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Constants This class contains constants that are used to get certain properties of jobs.
Enums A few enums used from the Grisu client library.
GridEnvironment Class to manage certain properties, caches that can be re-used by several grid client applications.
JSDLNamespaceContext A helper class to parse the jsdl document properly.
 

Enum Summary
Enums.LoginType Enums to specify which method to use to login to a Grisu backend.
Enums.UI Enums to determine the type of UI that is used to login.
JobSubmissionProperty Basic properties for a job that are needed to create a job.
 

Package grisu.jcommons.constants Description

Provides a location to set constants that may or not be used across several grid clients.
